481.title: Add authentication middleware
481.description: Implements JWT-based authentication for the API endpoints. Includes token generation and validation utilities.

482.title: Implement user model and database integration
482.description: Adds SQLAlchemy models for users and sets up PostgreSQL database connection pooling.

483.title: Update requirements and improve API handler
483.description: Updates dependencies to latest versions and adds new API endpoints for user management.

484.title: Implement basic quantum gates
484.description: Adds Pauli gates (X, Y, Z), Hadamard gate, and CNOT gate implementations with numpy backend.

485.title: Add Shor's and Grover's algorithms
485.description: Implements simplified versions of Shor's factorization algorithm and Grover's search algorithm.

486.title: Performance benchmarks and state vector optimization
486.description: Adds benchmarking suite for quantum simulations and optimizes state vector operations.

487.title: Core routing and middleware implementation
487.description: Implements HTTP router with path matching and request logging middleware.

488.title: Add load balancer and circuit breaker
488.description: Implements round-robin load balancer and circuit breaker pattern for fault tolerance.

489.title: Add health checks and metrics collection
489.description: Implements health check endpoints and Prometheus-compatible metrics collection.

490.title: Experimental GraphQL layer
490.description: Adds experimental GraphQL support for API queries. Needs review before merge.

491.title: [WIP] Database connection pooling
491.description: Work in progress: Implementing connection pooling for database optimization.

492.title: Hotfix: Token refresh race condition
492.description: Fixes a critical race condition in the JWT token refresh mechanism.

493.title: Quantum error correction codes
493.description: Implements basic quantum error correction using surface codes.

494.title: [Draft] Quantum machine learning primitives
494.description: Draft implementation of quantum machine learning algorithms including variational classifiers.

495.title: Release v1.0.0 preparation
495.description: Prepares codebase for v1.0.0 release with documentation updates and version bumps.

496.title: WebSocket support for real-time communication
496.description: Proposed WebSocket implementation. Closed due to scope creep - will be addressed in v2.0.

497.title: [WIP] gRPC gateway implementation
497.description: Work in progress draft for gRPC gateway support alongside REST API.

498.title: Hotfix: Memory leak in connection pool
498.description: Critical hotfix for memory leak when connections are not properly released.
